                  <td colspan="2" valign="top">No</td>
                  <td valign="top">Four stages: 1. Selection of states in the Niger River Basin; 2. Application of questionnaires to 360 farmers; 3 interviews with 12 key informants; 4. Observations of participants during field visits.</td>
                  <td colspan="2" valign="top">No</td>
                  <td valign="top">It focuses on the Niger River Basin, Nigeria.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td valign="top">[18]</td>
                  <td valign="top">[35]</td>
                  <td valign="top">No</td>
