                  <td valign="top">It uses quantitative methodology based on mathematical and computational models</td>
                  <td colspan="4" valign="top">Climate change include rising temperatures, ice and snow melting, sea level rise, and altered precipitation patterns</td>
                  <td colspan="2" valign="top"> </td>
